&"id": "1",
&"next_id": "2",
&"text": "Hey Naomi! Sorry about Nina 😅",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"10": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "10",
&"next_id": "11",
&"text": "What do you mean? 🤔",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"11": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "11",
&"next_id": "12",
&"text": "They have a way of \"befriending\" and pulling people in and before you know it you're part of their world",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"12": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "12",
&"next_id": "13",
&"text": "They prey on boys and girls alike... and they convince you into doing their erotic rites of passage",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"13": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "13",
&"next_id": "14",
&"text": "Before you know it, you're not even yourself anymore",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"14": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "14",
&"next_id": "15",
&"text": "Oh 😱 I'd be too scared to do any of that omg",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"15": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "15",
&"next_id": "16",
&"text": "But I have one question, what did she mean when she said \"afraid to lose someone else\"?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"16": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "16",
&"next_id": "17",
&"text": "I don't know how that Nina girl knows this actually",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"17": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "17",
&"next_id": "18",
&"text": "But she might be higher up in their chain of command I suppose",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"18": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "18",
&"next_id": "19",
&"text": "Basically.. My younger sister got recruited 😞",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"19": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "19",
&"next_id": "20",
&"text": "Oh no",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"2": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "2",
&"next_id": "3",
&"text": "Haha don't worry about it!",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"20": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "20",
&"next_id": "21",
&"text": "But that's my fault.. I should have been a better big sister and protected her",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"21": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "21",
&"next_id": "22",
&"text": "We used to be super close but then something happened and she didn't trust me anymore",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"22": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "22",
&"next_id": "23",
&"text": "Oh Naomi... I'm so sorry 🥺",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"23": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "23",
&"next_id": "24",
&"text": "It's okay, I'm still working on myself",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"24": {
&"character": "Naomi",
&"id": "24",
&"next_id": "25",
&"text": "I just don't want that happening to anyone else",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"25": {
&"character": "PlayerM",
&"id": "25",
&"next_id": "26",
&"text": "Well you're NOT losing me okay? 😤",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
