raw_text = "~ start
PlayerM: Hey Naomi! Sorry about Nina 😅
Naomi: Haha don't worry about it!
Naomi: But who was that sorority girl?
Naomi: How do you know her? 🤔
PlayerM: Oh that's Nina! We met during orientation
PlayerM: She kind of just came up to me and started talking
PlayerM: She's actually pretty nice once you get past the scary part 😅
Naomi: Hmm just be careful with those sorority girls okay?
Naomi: They're a bit on the crazy side
PlayerM: What do you mean? 🤔
Naomi: They have a way of \"befriending\" and pulling people in and before you know it you're part of their world
Naomi: They prey on boys and girls alike... and they convince you into doing their erotic rites of passage
Naomi: Before you know it, you're not even yourself anymore
PlayerM: Oh 😱 I'd be too scared to do any of that omg
PlayerM: But I have one question, what did she mean when she said \"afraid to lose someone else\"?
Naomi: I don't know how that Nina girl knows this actually
Naomi: But she might be higher up in their chain of command I suppose
Naomi: Basically.. My younger sister got recruited 😞
PlayerM: Oh no
Naomi: But that's my fault.. I should have been a better big sister and protected her
Naomi: We used to be super close but then something happened and she didn't trust me anymore
PlayerM: Oh Naomi... I'm so sorry 🥺
Naomi: It's okay, I'm still working on myself
Naomi: I just don't want that happening to anyone else
PlayerM: Well you're NOT losing me okay? 😤
PlayerM: You're stuck with me now 🩷
PlayerM: img: mabel/105
Naomi: 🥹 Thanks Mabel
Naomi: Now seriously, come check out the photography club 😂
Naomi: I'll have a seat with your name on it 😘
Naomi: img: naomi/17
PlayerM: Hehe okay okay I'll think about it!! 😊
=> END
"
